a waooo", "timestamp": 1774050959}, {"author": "charlesthomasprentice", "author_id": "31575476086", "id": "18041124815780547", "text": "How exciting, let's go!  Never fear, never despair, never surrender, that is exactly what they want.  We got this!  Let's become the quantum co-creators we are intended to be.  Love and light on your journey through life from Soquel Ca.  Love is the law of the universe.  We are all personifications of the Universe experiencing itself subjectively.  We are all L.O.V.E. Living One Vibrational Energy.  We are all one through the divinity of existence.  As above so below as within so without.  To thy own self be ever true as do as thou will is the whole of the law.  Namaste.", "timestamp": 1773812507}, {"author": "wrosario96", "author_id": "49120849976", "id": "18052495841706370", "text": "❤️❤️❤️❤️", "timestamp": 1773631310}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/590413503_1403501661387380_1526939536359115117_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEeP7sHgQWZv0b9CEYy8bwoypKQCq8av8k8ydhhmCVSbbpm7vZCFWM-h6sEvnlNaUY&_nc_ohc=Nypi9MPHyMcQ7kNvwGphpCz&_nc_gid=iEdCk2zJhfpWX5r25f5fWw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af2AgEJUKl4hLCUoQaDholY-jmsA63uymp5nELmxlR9gLg&oe=69D4BA7E&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/590413503_1403501661387380_1526939536359115117_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEeP7sHgQWZv0b9CEYy8bwoypKQCq8av8k8ydhhmCVSbbpm7vZCFWM-h6sEvnlNaUY&_nc_ohc=Nypi9MPHyMcQ7kNvwGphpCz&_nc_gid=iEdCk2zJhfpWX5r25f5fWw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af2AgEJUKl4hLCUoQaDholY-jmsA63uymp5nELmxlR9g